attributes.name: summary
attributes.value: Gemma 3 has emerged as the most powerful AI model capable of running on a single GPU or TPU, and it stands out as the first open-source model to surpass GPT-3.5.

attributes.name: summary
attributes.value: Gemini Robotics, developed by Google DeepMind, integrates advanced large language models with robotics to enhance their dexterity and functionality in interacting with the physical world.

attributes.name: summary
attributes.value: The new Gemini 2.0 Flash offers developers tools to experiment with native image generation, expanding possibilities for applications in Google AI Studio and through the Gemini API.

attributes.name: summary
attributes.value: Waabi's virtual robotrucks are so realistic that they can safely demonstrate the operational capabilities of driverless trucks without needing extensive on-road testing.
